us requirements igt complies with the principles of the international labor office’s tripartite declaration of principles concerning multinational enterprises and its social policy geneva  in particular the company complies with all of the recommendations in the aforementioned declaration with regard to relations with staff in the various states in july  gtech agreed to acquire american company international game technology igt the worlds largest slot machine manufacturer for a total of  billion including  billion in cash and  billion in assumed debt the companies combined under a new holding company based in the united kingdom and the gtech name was dropped in favor of igt on april   gtech completed its merger with igt the new combined companys name is international game technology plc referencesedit  a b c form f annual report report international game technology april   p f – via edgar   a b form f annual report report international game technology april   p f – via edgar   form f annual report report international game technology april   p  – via edgar   form f annual report report international game technology april   p  – via edgar   igtsustainabilityreport h retrieved    howard stutz  july  igt sold in  billion deal with lottery giant gtech las vegas reviewjournal retrieved    httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsgtechpannouncesnamecompanyhtml  httpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesgtechandinternationalgametechnologycompletecombinationandformtheworldsleadingendtoendgamingcompanyhtml external linksedit international game technology companies portal retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleinternationalgametechnologyoldid categories gambling companies of the united kingdomcompanies based in londoncompanies established in hidden categories use dmy dates from may official website different in wikidata and wikipedia navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search naviga