s from third parties such as wheel of fortune jeopardy life is good circuit of the americas ghostbusters gas monkey garage the three stooges plants v zombies bejeweled zuma caesars harrahs rio paris las vegas and horseshoe its lottery services are provided through concession or operator contracts also referred to as lottery management services arrangements facilities management contracts and product sales contracts igt plc supplies a range of solutions for online drawbased and instant ticket lotteries to over  customers across the world igt plc designs sells and operates a suite of lotteryenabled pointofsale terminals that are electronically linked with a centralized transaction processing system that reconciles lottery funds between the retailer where a transaction is enabled and the lottery authority among those solutions igt plc provides and operates online lottery transaction processing systems which are capable of processing over  transactions per minute igt plc provides over  pointofsale devices to lottery customers and lotteries that igt plc supports across the worldigt plc designs develops manufactures and provides cabinets games systems and software for customers in legal gaming markets throughout the world under fixed fee participation and product sales contracts igt plc holds over  global gaming licenses including from the nevada gaming commission igt plc offers a range of machine cabinets which landbased customers can choose in addition to cabinets igt plc develops a range of casino games taking into account local jurisdictional requirements market dynamics and player preferences igt plc casino games typically fall into approximately two categories including core games which include core video reel core mechanical reel and core video poker which are typically sold and in some situations leased to customers and premium games such as wide area progressives which are games that are linked across several casinos andor jurisdictions and share common jackpot and multilevel progressives which are linked to a number of other games within the casino itself and offer players the opportunity to win different levels of jackpots igt plc also produces other types of games including centrally determined games which are games connected to a central server that determines the game outcome and class  games which are electronic video bingo machines which can be found in north american tribal casinos and certain other jurisdictions such as south africa igt plc provides video lottery terminals vlt vlt central systems and vlt games to government customers across the world and provides vlt and games to operators across the world igt plc combines elements of math play mechanics sound art and technological advancements with a library of entertainment licenses and an intellectual property portfolio to provide its gaming products igt plc offers a range of system modules and applications for all areas of casino management its primary casino management system cms offering is the advantage system igt plc provides betting technology to lotteries and commercial operators in regulated markets primarily in italy and other countries in europeigt plc designs manufactures and distributes a suite of customizable products systems and services for internet gaming including internet poker table games slots bingo ilottery and gaming management systems gmss igt plcs online casino products include a range of table and slot games with single multiplayer and tournament play igt plcs bingo solution includes a social and interactive bingo live offering available in over four countries and in approximately four languages with the content adjusted to suit specific regions igt plcs suite of ilottery solutions services and professional knowhow allows lotteries to engage their players on any interactive channel in regulated markets igt plcs igaming systems cover every channel retail mobile and web and vertical from a degree view of the player web design and an engine to accelerate game content to customers websites igt plc also offers a remote games server igt plc offers a range of services to support interactive customers igt plc marketing intelligence services manages the player lifecycle to maximize player yield while ensuring the player is entertained and plays responsibly additionally igt plc provides player services including marketing portal player acquisition customer relationship management crm player support payment solutions fraud and collusion protection responsible gaming game management migration and trading servicesnorth america gaming and interactivethe nagi segment develops and delivers games systems and solutions for landbased casinos interactive forwager online play and the doubledown casino freetoplay social casino application the segment is responsible for research and development rd for commercial gaming products that are distributed to casinos throughout the world nagi provides a suite of casinorelated products and solutions to its commercial government and tribal customers in the united states and canada for landbased casino customers nagi provides company leadership in the development and distribution of global premium product including licensed content such as wheel of fortune slots in addition the global core product organization within nagi develops slot themes and video poker themes such as game king the nagi segment includes revenue from the sale or lease of commercial gaming machines and software to casinos and government entities in the united states and canada nagi also develops sells and licenses casino management systems these systems help casino customers to manage operational efficiencies and player engagement by delivering personalized player amenities and promotional offers additionally service revenue is generated for commercial gaming from the maintenance of machines and systems nagi also generates revenue from its doubledown casino social casino application where customers purchase virtual currency for use in nonwagering interactive games play for fun played over the internet including desktop and mobile devices its crossplatform content delivery system igt casino remote game server enables igaming operators of forwager online interactive properties to access the companys content library to provide players with their favorite casino content on desktop and mobile devices its global operations organization including global manufacturing operations is based in reno nevada and is the primary manufacturer of all nagi products in addition to various other products for other igt business segments such as lotterynorth america lotterythe north america lottery segment develops and delivers lottery solutions this business segment provides north america world lottery association wla customers with a single point of contact leveraging igt plcs lottery product suite igt plc supports over  of the  united states lotteries north america lottery performs rd for all lotteryrelated products across the world north america lottery includes revenue related to the sale or lease of lottery central system hardware and software and the sale or lease of lottery and gaming terminals to government entities igt plc also has lottery management agreements in approximately three united states jurisdictions including illinois indiana and new jerseythe north america lottery segment includes revenue generated from the sale of physical instant tickets to government entities governmentsponsored lotteries grant printing contracts on both an exclusive and nonexclusive basis where there is typically a primary vendor and one or more secondary vendors a primary contract permits the vendor to supply the majority of the lotterys ticket printing needs and includes the production process from concept development through production and shipment it also typically includes marketing and research support a primary printing contract can also include various services such as warehousing distribution telemarketing and salesfield support a secondary printing contract includes providing backup printing services and alternate product sources it may or may not include a guarantee of a minimum or maximum number of gamesinternationalthe international segment is engaged in delivering endtoend solutions across all channels and regulated gaming segments this segment is responsible for the strategic development and operation management for all markets in europe the middle east central and latin america including mexico the caribbean asia pacific and oceania across igt plcs entire product portfolio its global strategy capitalizes on its north america experience while customizing products for foreign languages local preferences and regulatory requirementsthe international segment includes revenue from the sale or lease of commercial gaming machines and software to casinos and government entities and from the sale or hosting or realmoney interactive wagering games played over the internet this segment also includes revenue from the sale or lease of lottery central system hardware and software and the sale or lease of lottery terminals to government entities additionally the segment includes revenue from the sale of physical instant tickets to government entities and professional services in the form of lottery facility management and lottery operation fees legalized online realmoney gaming in certain regulated international markets also continues to make a contribution igt plc offers various interactive gaming products within the international segment including poker casino bingo and mobile systemsitalythe italy segment derives revenue from lottery and machine gaming concessions the italy segment operates and provides a range of bc gaming products including over five product lines such as lottery which includes the operation of instant and traditional lotteries machine gaming which operates in the machine gaming concession in italy sports betting which includes sports events and nonsports events connected with current affairs commercial services which offers transaction processing of commercial transactions collection and payment services money transfer services fidelity card services and stamp duty services and interactive gaming which provides games authorized in the italian market including skill games and other board and soft gamesthe company competes with  holdings bwinparty playtech plc microgaming software systems scientific games corporation amaya gaming caesars zynga bet snai eurobet intralot sa pollard banknote limited eagle press of india tattersalls sisal spa aristocrat leisure limited konami sazka opap sa and camelot » full overview of igtn company address international game technology plc second flmarble arch house  seymour stlondon     wh bt p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation philip satre  marco sala  patti hart  lorenzo pellicioli  alberto fornaro  » more officers  directors international game technology plc news briefigt announces new term loan facility and amendment to multicurrency revolving credit facilities jul   briefigt signs threeyear contract extension with the new york lottery jul   briefigt awarded yr contract with the west virginia lottery jun   briefinternational game technology announces results of tender offer for  mln  pct notes due  jun   briefigt signs crosslicensing agreement with konami gaming inc jun   » more igtn news related topics stocksstock screenercasinos  gaming international game technology  wikipedia international game technology from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search for the company acquired by gtech see international game technology  international game technology plc type public traded as nyse igt industry gaming founded  headquarters london england headquarters las vegas nevada operating offices providence rhode island operating offices rome italy operating offices key people marco sala ceo phil satre chairman products slot mach